{"lastModified":1772813389860,"uri":"c::7818345123::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nS/Cat Omnia, Lagoon 46, was built in 2020! She can accommodate 8 guests in 4 cabins. A crew of two are in different compartments.\n\nOmnia combines comfort and luxury. She is fully air conditioned , with a generator. She also has a water maker available, Cigars Humidor, Wine Refrigerator, USB sockets in cabins, Inverter 2000W, WiFi on board, TV, Audio system, Dishwasher, Nespresso coffee machine,2 x large drawer refrigerators and freezer, Toaster, Electric kettle and full deluxe kitchenware equipment.","blueprint":{"name":"OMNIA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e1fd6060-fc31-11ee-9dd0-69008535a640.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4c98f250-ea06-11ef-a5b1-37420af0e92a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e93ead20-fc31-11ee-9dd0-69008535a640.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::437d4040-ea06-11ef-a5b1-37420af0e92a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e93efb40-fc31-11ee-9dd0-69008535a640.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e93fbe90-fc31-11ee-9dd0-69008535a640.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e93f9780-fc31-11ee-9dd0-69008535a640.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e93fe5a0-fc31-11ee-9dd0-69008535a640.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e94033c0-fc31-11ee-9dd0-69008535a640.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f