"},{"label":"Toaster"},{"label":"Electric kettle"},{"label":"Kitchenware equipment"},{"label":"Fly bridge lounge upper deck"},{"label":"Forward sunpad"},{"label":"Electric winch"},{"label":"Hydraulic gangway"},{"label":"Cockpit refrigerator"},{"label":"Solar panel"},{"label":"Underwater lights"}],"toys":[{"label":"SUP","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Canoe- Kayak (2 seated inflatable)"},{"label":"Troll fishing rod"},{"label":" Sea Scooter Jobe","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Towable Single tube","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Towable Double Person Ring","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Snorkeling gear"},{"label":"Adult water ski","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Wake Surf Board","quantity":"1"}],"entertainment":["WiFi on board","TV","Audio System","Karaoke 40W 2 microphones","Bluetooth 40W Speaker"],"tenders":["Powerful tender 40hp"]},"crew":[{"name":"Lampros Charis","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7253b800-ea05-11ef-aae5-ad69c94350ea/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Lampros was born and raised in Patras. He is a very enthusiastic and experienced captain, born in 1986, and his sailing career spans thousand of sailing miles in the Greek seas and the Mediterranean. His participation in various major sailing championships has equipped him with a lot of experience and discipline required in this type of work, while he holds a Yacht Master Offshore RYA / MCA license.\n\nLampros has worked on superyachts for many years and has sailed in all the waters of Greece and most part of the Mediterranean. He knows very well how to provide a five-star service to his clients and that compromise in not an option.\n\nLampros is fluent in English and his mother tongue is Greek.\n\nIn his free time Lampros is ether on top of a mountain skiing or else in the sea windsurfing or taking part in sailing competitions."},{"name":"Rozina Geldari","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4f85-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::91256da0-ea05-11ef-953f-8562af482836/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Rozina was born in 1990 and grew up in Piraeus. Her initial studies where in Economics but her creative and passionate personality made her pursue a different career that led her to the tourism industry . Rozina has worked for 7 years in luxury hotels and restaurants where she was in charge of preparing breakfast and lunches for large numbers of groups. She is very passionate about her work and is an exceptional host always providing top service to her guests. Rozina loves making sweets and cooking the Greek Mediterranean cuisine using fresh products and introducing her guests to a variety of tasty dishes. Rozina has a lovely and warm personality and is always there to attend to her guests needs.\n\nShe speaks English and Greek.\n\nRozina spends her free time with her 6 year old daughter , she enjoys reading books and travelling."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":1270000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":1270000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":1580000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":1580000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Weekly Rate: July and August","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":1580000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":1580000,"amount":1580000,"conditions":"Weekly","taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.12}},{"item":"APA","conditions":"","quantity":0.3,"unitPrice":1580000,"amount":474000}],"total":2243600,"subTotal":2054000,"totalTax":189600},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Greece","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Greece"],"coordinates":[24.261736188816826,38.42232351533858],"bbox":[19.646484375,34.934472656249994,28.231835937500023,41.743798828124994]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"name":"Weekly Rate: June and September","effectiveDa